<p>What are We going to Learn Today!
We are going to Use <a href="https://jekyllrb.com/">Jekyll</a>, a Static Site creator, and <a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a>, a software hosting platform.
I am also using a Jekyll Theme: <a href="https://github.com/jekyll/minima">Minima</a>, which is the default theme, but I have altered it to make it my own.
